{"article_id":"k5nSpKBAM5EyB8HW","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"RICHMOND , Va. -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Democrats couldn ' t react fast enough to the racist photo in Virginia Gov . Ralph Northam ' s old yearbook","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"showing one man","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"dressed as a Klansman","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and another in blackface .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"But a newly surfaced sexual assault allegation against the man","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"who would replace Northam","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"if he resigns","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"- Justin Fairfax , the state ' s African-American lieutenant governor and a rising star in the party -","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"has left Democratic national figures and Virginia lawmakers at a loss for words .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"The back-to-back stunners in Richmond exposed fault lines in the Democratic Party coalition","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"that were unimaginable just five days ago .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"And with the state ' s political hierarchy in the balance , the stories triggered a potential collision of two powerful forces in Democratic politics","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"- the battle","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to combat racism","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"and the movement","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"to stop sexual harassment .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Swift to condemn Northam on Friday ,","depth":4},{"id":18,"text":"Democratic presidential hopefuls ducked for cover on Tuesday .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"Sen. Bernie Sanders clung to an apparent cellphone call in the Capitol","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"to avoid a reporter ' s questions about Fairfax .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Other Democratic senators","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"- who both condemned Northam","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"it was imperative to \" believe the woman \"","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"when Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh was accused of sexual harassment -","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"have gone silent , too .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Playbook newsletter","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Sign up today","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to receive the # 1-rated newsletter in politics","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"By signing up","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" I ' m really not going to comment , \"","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"said Tina Tchen , past chief of staff for former first lady Michelle Obama and a co-founder of a new legal defense group for sexual harassment victims","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"called Time ' s Up .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"\" I don ' t know enough about Virginia , \"","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"\" The stories are certainly messy","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"if you want me to comment about the lieutenant governor ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"I don ' t know enough . \"","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Tchen added later","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that \" the TIME ' S UP Legal Defense Fund takes the accusations of all survivors seriously","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"and so should everyone else . \"","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Fairfax has called the allegation a politically motivated \" smear \"","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"timed to damage him on the cusp of the governorship .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"In Richmond , Democratic lawmakers","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"who over the past five days pushed for Northam ' s resignation","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"were quietly milling around the state capitol on Tuesday ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"ducking out of legislative sessions via side doors","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"to avoid the media","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and responding to questions with \" no comment. \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"With Northam showing no signs","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"of resigning ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"and Democrats and Republicans alike unsure of how to respond to the emerging sexual assault claim against Fairfax ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"lawmakers tried to avoid the scandal .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Late in the day on Tuesday , Democrats in the Legislature issued a joint statement","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"responding to the harassment allegation ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"that \" the facts here are still being determined . \"","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"\" Every individual deserves the opportunity","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"to be heard ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"and we respect anyone","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"who comes forward","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"to share their story , \"","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"the statement read .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"The state ' s Democratic senators , Tim Kaine and Mark Warner ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"who have both called on Northam to resign ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"expressed a need for caution in response to the allegation against Fairfax .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" With respect to the situation with the lieutenant governor , I just don ' t know enough information , \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Kaine told CNN on Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"\" He has seen the reports","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and that the lieutenant governor denies","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"anything nonconsensual occurred , \"","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"a Warner spokesperson told .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"\" Senator Warner believes","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"every allegation deserves to be heard","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"and taken seriously . \"","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"A major difference between the two controversies","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"- Northam ' s blackface and the assault claim against Fairfax -","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"is the nature of the evidence .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Northam initially admitted Friday","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"he was one of two young men","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"depicted in blackface or a Klan outfit on his 1984 medical school yearbook page .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"He then recanted that admission at a news conference Saturday afternoon ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"he had donned blackface","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"to imitate Michael Jackson on another occasion at a talent show .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"With respect to the sexual assault allegations , there is a dispute over what happened between Fairfax and his accuser ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"though both agree","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"they had a sexual encounter .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"She told The Washington Post","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that Fairfax forced her to perform sexual acts on him during the Democratic National Convention in 2004 .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"The Post could not corroborate the story","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"and initially chose not to publish it .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"A social media post about the incident was later leaked to the website Big League Politics","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"and published online .","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"Fairfax has repeatedly denied the allegation ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"first in a statement","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"posted overnight on Monday","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"in which he said","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"he has \" never assaulted anyone. \"","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"He has called the allegation \" completely false \"","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"and said","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"that he kept in touch with the woman after the incident .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"is not naming the accuser","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"out of respect for her privacy .","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"She has hired the law firm of Katz , Marshall and Banks ,","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"which represented Kavanaugh accuser Christine Blasey Ford .","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"Democrats ' wait-and-see approach","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"to handling the allegation against Fairfax","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"reflects an unpleasant truth :","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"The party has no playbook","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"for how to respond to claims of sexual harassment or assault .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"\" It ' s a mess , \"","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"said one consultant","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"who has been communicating with the lieutenant governor ' s team .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"\" And it ' s indicative of challenges","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"we face in 2020","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"when we talk about race and gender and balancing the two .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"It ' s emblematic of what ' s to come . \"","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"There are also practical concerns","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"over how the party will proceed in Richmond in the coming weeks .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Fairfax was widely expected to replace Northam","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"if the latter resigned from office .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"If he is not able to replace Northam ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"then Virginia Attorney General Mark Herring is the most likely replacement","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"if both the governor and lieutenant governor were to resign from office .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Such a situation is unimaginable to Virginia operatives ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"especially with Northam resisting the drumbeat of calls","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"to resign .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"But the sudden uncertainty about the line of succession has fed a sense of paralysis within the state Capitol","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"about what ' s next and how to respond .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"An attorney","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"who briefly represented another Kavanaugh accuser , one-time Democratic presidential hopeful Michael Avenatti ,","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Ford gained credibility by the way","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"she calmly and clearly spoke out publicly against Kavanaugh ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"which gave rise to Democrats ' \" believe the woman \" mantra .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"he would reserve judgment in Fairfax ' s case ,","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"but acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"there ' s a disparity in the reaction to the two cases","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"because of partisan politics .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"\" There ' s no question","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"that it ' s incredibly difficult for her to come forward , especially in a high-profile situation such as this , \"","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"Avenatti said","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"when asked about the challenges","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"presented by a progressive African-American woman","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"accusing a black Democratic politician of sexual assault .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"Avenatti said","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"Fairfax ' s accuser needs to be heard from .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"But he said","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"the situation is risky .","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"\" It takes someone to have incredible courage","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"because they put their life on the line , both literally and figuratively , \"","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"Avenatti said .","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"\" Their lives are never the same . \"","d